@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "Platform Operator" as operator
actor "Workflow Observer" as observer
actor "Manual Fallback User" as fallback

rectangle "REQ-012 v2 — LLM Orchestrator Replaces Event Bus" {
  (Create Group with Workflow) as UC1
  (Start Group) as UC2
  (Observe Workflow Progress) as UC3
  (Attach to Pane) as UC4
  (View Actionable Error Message) as UC5
  (Force Advance Stalled Worker) as UC6
  (Abort Workflow) as UC7
  (Acknowledge Schema Reset Modal) as UC8
}

operator --> UC1
operator --> UC2
operator --> UC4
operator --> UC5
operator --> UC8

observer --> UC3
observer --> UC4

fallback --> UC6
fallback --> UC7
fallback --> UC4

UC1 ..> UC2 : precedes
UC2 ..> UC3 : enables
UC3 ..> UC6 : on stall
UC3 ..> UC7 : on stall

note right of UC1
  Workflow dropdown:
  - standard (PM->TD->Dev->Tester->User)
  - prototype (Dev->User)
  - research (PM->TD->User)
  REQ-009 auto-creates 6 agents
  including Orchestrator (F-11)
end note

note right of UC2
  Workers start first; orchestrator
  starts last after all workers
  reach 'active' (F-04)
end note

note right of UC3
  Orchestrator pane shows the live
  workflow state; AgentPane badges
  show "current step" (F-07/F-08)
end note

note right of UC6
  Triggered by ORCHESTRATOR_STALL_TIMEOUT
  (default 10 min) after dispatch with
  no completion signal (F-09 tertiary)
end note

note bottom of UC8
  First-run after upgrade: schema
  version mismatch -> destructive
  reset of .agent_management/ (Section 4)
end note
@enduml
